com.cc.systems

Class Mechanism

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cc.systems.Mechanism

  • public class Mechanism
extends Object
    This class represents the Mechanism on the robot and is responsible for operating the shooter and the pick-up mechanism of the robot.
